T1  - On the flexibility of flexible functional forms: An empirical approach∗∗I am indebted to W.E. Diewert, R.A. Pollak and A.D. Woodland for helpful comments and to Norine Smith for exceptional research assistance.
AU  - Wales, Terence J.
